<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='759000' id='t-759000'>And so we expect -- it's not much fun.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763000' id='t-763000'>We expect, and others expect,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='766000' id='t-766000'>that perhaps the FAA, the CAA</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='768000' id='t-768000'>might say, &quot;You need to put someone in a suit</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='770000' id='t-770000'>that's not inflated, that's connected to the aircraft.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='773000' id='t-773000'>Then they're comfortable, they have good vision, like this great big visor.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='776000' id='t-776000'>And then if the cabin depressurizes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='778000' id='t-778000'>while the aircraft is coming back down,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='780000' id='t-780000'>in whatever emergency measures, everyone is okay.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:13
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='782000' id='t-782000'>I would like to bring Costa on, if he's here,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='785000' id='t-785000'>to show you the only one of its kind in the world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='788000' id='t-788000'>I was going to wear it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='790000' id='t-790000'>but I thought I'd get Costa to do it, my lovely assistant.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='792000' id='t-792000'>Thank you. He's very hot. Thank you, Costa.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='797000' id='t-797000'>This is the communication headset you'll see</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='800000' id='t-800000'>on lots of space suits.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='802000' id='t-802000'>It's a two-layer suit. NASA suits have got 13 layers.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='806000' id='t-806000'>This is a very lightweight suit. It weighs about 15 pounds.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='810000' id='t-810000'>It's next to nothing. Especially designed for me.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:43
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='812000' id='t-812000'>It's a working prototype. I will use it for all the jumps.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='814000' id='t-814000'>Would you just give us a little twirl, please, Costa?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='817000' id='t-817000'>Thank you very much.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='819000' id='t-819000'>And it doesn't look far different when it's inflated,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='821000' id='t-821000'>as you can see from the picture down there.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='823000' id='t-823000'>I've even skydived in it in a wind tunnel,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='826000' id='t-826000'>which means that I can practice everything I need to practice, in safety,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='829000' id='t-829000'>before I ever jump out of anything. Thanks very much, Costa.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='831000' id='t-831000'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='835000' id='t-835000'>Ladies and gentlemen, that's just about it from me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='837000' id='t-837000'>The status of my mission at the moment</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='839000' id='t-839000'>is it still needs a major sponsor.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='841000' id='t-841000'>I'm confident that we'll find one.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='843000' id='t-843000'>I think it's a great challenge.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='845000' id='t-845000'>And I hope that you will agree with me,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='847000' id='t-847000'>it is the greatest stunt on Earth.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='850000' id='t-850000'>Thank you very much for your time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='852000' id='t-852000'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
